data.description: Drink in the incredible views of the Missouri River, Park Island and the Meadowlark Country Club beyond! You'll love living at 1 Volk Terrace with it's timeless architectural features and prime location. Majestic windows let in tons of natural light and the vaulted ceilings w/ exposed beams add just the perfect touch! The master wing provides river views, two spacious closets and a generous master bathroom. Enjoy your dinner fireside with the two-sided fireplace situated between the formal and informal dining rooms. Hardwood floors, updated appliances, built in shelves, two living rooms, new windows and ample storage space all within a great neighborhood with easy access to shopping, schools, parks and all that Great Falls has to offer. Don't miss this impressive 5 bed, 3.5 bath home!
